ata evamādigranthavighaṭanenāgamavirodhāt tṛtīye vikalparūpo vimardo naiṣitavyaḥ | yatas tatra nirvikalpakavedanam evāste | <commentary>tad eva sopaskāram upasaṃharati—

vilakṣaṇam ityādi | subodham ||

nanu lokaprasiddhibādhāyā abādhakatvāt katham "ālocanaṃ vimardaś cet" ityādinā bādhā darśitā | tad etad api bhavato 'asmadabhiprāyāparijñānaphalam | yato "viramānandaṃ jagac caiva" iti vimardasya jagadrūpatayā prastutabādhanena yathoktasarvāgamavighaṭanāt | ālocanam ityādigrantho 'pi vighaṭata evety ata ālocanam ityādinā bādhā darśitā | ata evāryanāgārjunapādair api caturmudrānvaye—

	paramaviramayor madhye lakṣyam vīkṣya dṛḍhīkuru |

iti bādhā darśitā | tarhi tvanmate

	ānandena sukhaṃ kiñcit paramānandaṃ tato 'dhikam |
	viramānandair virāgaḥ syāt sahajānandas tu śeṣataḥ || 

iti katham | tad apy evaṃ jñeyam | ānandaparamaviramaiḥ kiñcitsukhatadadhikavirāgāṇāṃ grahaṇāc cheṣataḥ pāriśeṣyatas tribhyo anyatayā sahajānando boddhavyaḥ | yadvānandaparamaviramasahaja ity anukramavaśād evam uktam | boddhavyas tu tṛtīya eva sahajaḥ |

yady evaṃ kuto bhagavatā suṣeka eva na darśitaḥ | kim ity āyāsabahulahaṭhasekaśaṅkāspadam ānandaparamaviramasahaja iti kramo darśitaḥ | tan na | pustakapāṇḍityanirāsakalyāṇamitrādhīnārthatvād eva kramadarśanasya | tad uktam—"kalyāṇamitrādhīnā hi bodhiḥ" | tathānyatra—"guruṇā tuṣṭena labhyate" iti | kiṃ cettham āgamavirodhena haṭhasekaṃ duḥsekaṃ ca dūṣayatā nirākārādivyavsthā na dūṣitaiva | tasyā āyojanamātrasya viruddhatvāt | ato nikhilavyavastheyaṃ vajradharāśvāsarūpasuṣekasiddhānta eva veditavyā | svasiddhānte haṭhaduḥsekavādino 'py evaṃ varṇayantīty etadartham atra darśitā ||</commentary>

etad anantaraṃ duḥsekam āha—cumbanetyādi | darśanam ārabhya ghṛṣṭeḥ pūrvaṃ yāvad bāhyakriyā vicitram | bolakakkolayogāt prabhṛti śaśino maṇeḥ pūrvaṃ yāvad āgamanaṃ ghṛṣṭis tatra vipākaḥ |
